&gt;��- half-{T} = {F} (vague visual similarity between _F_&lt;br&gt;
&gt;��and _T_)&lt;br&gt;
&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&gt;��And in addition:&lt;br&gt;
&gt;
    &lt;br&gt;
&gt;��- half-{d} = {�} (_Ed_)&lt;br&gt;
