&gt;��&lt;&lt;a moz-do-not-send=&quot;true&quot;
 href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/British_and_American_keyboards&quot;&gt;http://en.wikipedia&lt;wbr&gt;.org/wiki/&lt;wbr&gt;British_and_&lt;wbr&gt;American_&lt;wbr&gt;keyboards&lt;/a&gt;&gt;.
    &lt;br&gt;
&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&gt;��Last but not least: I am among those who find the&lt;br&gt;
&gt;��assignment of alt-{n} to _q_ bothersome, but I have&lt;br&gt;
